<title>网友实测三星Galaxy S20 Ultra相机能力：100倍变焦强悍</title>
<link>https://www.ithome.com/0/474/861.htm</link>
<guid>https://www.ithome.com/0/474/861.htm</guid>
<description>
<![CDATA[
<p>IT之家2月26日消息&nbsp;最新发布的三星Galaxy S20系列无论是屏幕、处理器、内存还是摄像头都是安卓旗舰新标杆的存在，该机在相机方面相比前代产品也有了极大的提高，<span class="accentTextColor">搭载了1.08亿像素的主摄，更是支持100倍混合变焦</span>。</p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095903_917.jpg" w="602" h="477"/></p><p>三星S20 Ultra配备矩阵式后置四摄，其中主摄1.08亿像素，0.8微米像素尺寸，支持九像素合一等效于1200万像素输出，79度广角，F1.8固定光圈，OIS光学防抖，支持100倍变焦。4800万像素长焦镜头像素尺寸0.8微米，光圈F3.5，OIS光学防抖，5倍光学变焦；1200万像素120的超广角镜头，像素尺寸1.4微米，光圈F2.2；此外还有一个ToF镜头。</p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_101828_365.jpg" w="599" h="644"/></p><p>▲这位博主估计是在开玩笑：）</p><p>据IT之家了解，三星Galaxy S20 Ultra用上了自研的潜望式光学变焦模组，可以实现10倍光变和高达100倍的数码变焦，横放时的厚度仅有5mm。</p><p>IT之家发现近期在社交媒体上不断有知名数码博主和S20 Ultra用户放出该机的100倍变焦样张，一起来看一下吧：</p><p>来自于Marques Brownlee：</p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095815_57.jpg" w="600" h="450"/></p><p>1x</p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095815_448.jpg" w="600" h="450"/></p><p>5x</p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095815_589.jpg" w="600" h="450"/></p><p>30x</p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095815_729.jpg" w="600" h="450"/></p><p>100x</p><p>来自于GadgetMatch：</p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095815_854.jpg" w="600" h="800"/></p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095816_73.jpg" w="600" h="800"/></p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095816_901.jpg" w="600" h="800"/></p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095817_167.jpg" w="600" h="800"/></p><p>来自于Canoopsy：</p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095817_323.jpg" w="600" h="450"/></p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095817_542.jpg" w="600" h="450"/></p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095817_854.jpg" w="600" h="450"/></p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095818_57.jpg" w="600" h="450"/></p><p>来自于Canoopsy：</p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095818_260.jpg" w="600" h="450"/></p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095818_448.jpg" w="600" h="450"/></p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095818_667.jpg" w="600" h="450"/></p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095818_807.jpg" w="600" h="450"/></p><p>来自于&nbsp;Thao Huynh：</p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095818_932.jpg" w="600" h="800"/></p><p>0.5x</p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095819_198.jpg" w="600" h="800"/></p><p>1x</p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095819_474.jpg" w="600" h="800"/></p><p>5x</p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095819_744.jpg" w="600" h="800"/></p><p>10x</p><p>来自于&nbsp;Andrew Martonik：</p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095820_73.jpg" w="600" h="450"/></p><p>1x</p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095820_229.jpg" w="600" h="450"/></p><p>10x</p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095820_385.jpg" w="600" h="450"/></p><p>30x</p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_095820_698.jpg" w="600" h="450"/></p><p>100x</p>
