<title>搭载骁龙865，OPPO Find X2 Pro开启预约</title>
<link>https://www.ithome.com/0/474/837.htm</link>
<guid>https://www.ithome.com/0/474/837.htm</guid>
<description>
<![CDATA[
<p>IT之家2月26日消息&nbsp;OPPO Find X2系列旗舰手机昨日宣布，将于3月6日全球首发。据IT之家网友反馈，OPPO Find X2 Pro现已开启预约。</p><p>这也确认了，OPPO Find X2系列包括OPPO Find X2与OPPO Find X2 Pro两款机型。预约界面显示，OPPO Find X2 Pro支持移动\联通\电信5G与双卡双待功能。</p><p><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2020/2/20200226_073030_118.jpg" w="728" h="608"/></p><p>爆料信息显示，OPPO Find X2与OPPO Find X2 Pro均搭载高通骁龙865移动平台，支持SA、NSA双模5G，采用6.7英寸屏幕，支持120Hz刷新率与1200nit最高亮度，拥有100% DCI-P3色域覆盖。</p><p>IT之家了解到，OPPO Find X2 Pro预计采用48MP + 48MP + 13MP后置三摄方案，全球首发全像素全向对焦技术，CIS尺寸有望达到1/1.33英寸，支持65W SuperVOOC闪充与30W无线快充。</p><dir><a href="https://union-click.jd.com/jdc?e=&p=AyIGZRprFQMTBlUbXh0EEw9QKx9KWkxYZUIeUENQDEsFA1BWThgOTkRHXE4ZVRpaFAISAl0dWh0HDV4QRwYlQ3Z3AH0uXkJwb1IBAFcGRGY9WA5xYh4LZRhcHAsUN1YZXBcEFgJWHGtfEWZSDV4FVhEZFICS6sCKtRQZK1sWMkRpVRpaFAMTAlQcXyUCEQBRGV4dAxoPZRtfHAEVDlQaWhACFQRlG1MSMk5FB1oZJTIiBGUraxUyEjcKXwZIMhAGVBlZ" target="_blank" data-wapurl="https://union-click.jd.com/jdc?e=&p=AyIGZRprFQMTBlUbXh0EEw9QKx9KWkxYZUIeUENQDEsFA1BWThgOTkRHXE4ZVRpaFAISAl0dWh0HDV4QRwYleEZxFkwEawFwUQETEnxSaHUPWj5HYh4LZR5aHQoXAFUcWCUBEABXHV8QARU3HwgvQFpXWRYIUAbXm7aAk%2FwGTiIHUCsNewITBlQaWhADFQNlG18QBxsGVRNcEzISA1wYXBwDEwZQGFkdMhIPUisHV1BTRWUraxYyIjdVK1slXVZaCCtZFAMQBQ%3D%3D" data-iosurl="https://union-click.jd.com/jdc?e=&p=AyIGZRprFQMTBlUbXh0EEw9QKx9KWkxYZUIeUENQDEsFA1BWThgOTkRHXE4ZVRpaFAISAl0dWh0HDV4QRwYlW2kPEmkuRX9yWVZZRVVFEWFTTxl%2BVB4LZRtZFQoRBlUaWB0yEQVSGV0RBxEAZVFIYVdKQgtYSB4Rx47kztOyEV43VRprQ2wSBlQaWhQHEwBRK1sWBRYFURtaHQoiB1ESWBILEwZUHlkVAiIHXRxrSUBARhcrayUBIjdlG2sVMk1DCEZrFwMTBVc%3D" data-androidurl="https://union-click.jd.com/jdc?e=&p=AyIGZRprFQMTBlUbXh0EEw9QKx9KWkxYZUIeUENQDEsFA1BWThgOTkRHXE4ZVRpaFAISAl0dWh0HDV4QRwYlXBF8NFIycnpxby97GBZCR0JdTlxoYh4LZR5aHQoXAFUcWCUBEABXHV8QARU3HwgvQFpXWRYIUAbXm7aAk%2FwGTiIHUCsNewITBlQaWhADFQNlG1gSBhACXRtbETISA1wYXBwDEwZQGVwVMhIPUisHV1BTRWUraxYyIjdVK1slXVZaCCtZFAMQBQ%3D%3D" data-uwpurl="https://union-click.jd.com/jdc?e=&p=AyIGZRprFQMTBlUbXh0EEw9QKx9KWkxYZUIeUENQDEsFA1BWThgOTkRHXE4ZVRpaFAISAl0dWh0HDV4QRwYlAhplS2xYb3twXStmPlYC